node.text: In case you missed it, we went live with Dr. Maya Warren for National Ice Cream Day! Check out how to assemble a chartreaterie board using Cold Stone ice cream and mix-ins you have at home.

node.title: National Ice Cream Day with @coldstone Tastemaster
